 (March 30, 1915). Title varies slightly as: Weekly Elko independent, Mar. 19, 1964-Dec. 31, 1964. Supplements accompany some issues. Description based on: Forty-eighth year, no. 74 (March 30, 1915); title from masthead (Chroniclingamerica.loc.gov, viewed April 4, 2018). Latest issue consulted: Fifty-third year, no. 73 (June 21, 1921) (Chroniclingamerica.loc.gov, viewed April 4, 2018)."], "digitized": true, "extract_timestamp": "2026-05-19T21:37:42.357Z", "group": ["ndnp/newspapers", "united-states-newspaper-directory"], "hassegments": false, "id": "http://www.loc.gov/item/2018218670/", "image_url": [], "index": 7, "language": ["english"], "location": ["united states", "nevada", "elko"], "number": ["2026-04-13t21:30:13", "1030440556", "2577-5332", "online resource", "2018218669", "2018218670"], "original_format": ["newspaper"], "other_title": ["Weekly Elko independent"], "partof": ["elko independent (elko, elko county, nevada) 1915-current [online resource]", "directory of u.s. newspapers in american libraries", "serial and government publications division"], "publication_frequency": ["weekly"], "score": 38.582832, "shelf_id": "ISSN RECORD", "site": ["usnd"], "subject": ["newspapers", "nevada", "elko", "elko (nev.)", "united states"], "timestamp": "2026-05-26T20:56:09.337Z", "title": "Elko independent", "type": ["title"], "url": "https://www.loc.gov/item/2018218670/"}], "next_resource": {"label": "Next Issue", "url": "https://www.loc.gov/resource/sn84020355/1913-12-31/ed-1/?fo=json&sp=1"}, "options": {"access_group": [""], "access_group_raw": "", "all": null, "api_version": "1", "app_context": null, "application_version": "$Revision$", "attribute": null, "attribute!": null, "attribute_map": null, "cache_tags": ["ndnp/nvln", "university-of-nevada-las-vegas-university-libraries-awardee", "newspaper-titles", "catalog-split-12", "catalog", "ndnp/newspapers", "main-catalog-split-12", "united-states-newspaper-directory", "afc/ofp/2011064", "catalog-split-06", "western-fol